OL,3,CHomeless grandmother has spent 19
OL,4,Cmonths living in Premier Inn
OL,6,FIt's been 19 months since Annette
OL,7,FWilkinson checked into Bude's Premier
OL,8,FInn after a relationship breakdown.
OL,10,FEvery day that passes she says she
OL,11,Fsays she is losing faith.
OL,13,F"I really didn't see any light at the
OL,14,Fend of the tunnel because I just can't
OL,15,Feven imagine me being in somewhere,
OL,16,Fbecause it's been so long and my
OL,17,Fmental health is just in bits," she
OL,18,Fsaid.
