OL,3,CHomeless grandmother has spent 19
OL,4,Cmonths living in Premier Inn
OL,6,FThe grandmother moved to the North
OL,7,FCornwall town six years ago to be
OL,8,Fcloser to family.
OL,10,FBut, having now spent more than a year
OL,11,Fand a half in emergency accommodation,
OL,12,Fher health is now deteriorating, her
OL,13,Fbeloved cats are living in foster
OL,14,Fcare, and she says she is "in tears
OL,15,Fall the time".
OL,1,W~s1j5 hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}      G2/9
