OL,3,CHomeless grandmother has spent 19
OL,4,Cmonths living in Premier Inn
OL,6,FSally said: "She looks drained. She
OL,7,Fcomes in and she tries to put on a
OL,8,Fbrave face, but you know that she's
OL,9,Freally upset and battling against it.
OL,10,Fbut she knows we're all here to help
OL,11,Fif we can. But you can't do much about
OL,12,Fit really can you?"
OL,14,FAdding further upset Annette now looks
OL,15,Fset to lose her four cats who have
OL,16,Fbeen cared for by a foster charity.
