OL,6,F"I got a formal letter from them a
OL,7,Fcouple of days ago that states I've
OL,8,Fgot four weeks notice now. I have have
OL,9,Fto collect them within four weeks and
OL,10,Fif I don't I'm going to lose them.
OL,12,F"My cats are the longest they've ever
OL,13,Fhad any animal. It's not fair on them
OL,14,Fbeing in foster care and they need the
OL,15,Fspace."
