OL,4,Cmonths living in Premier Inn
OL,6,FA spokesperson for Cornwall Housing
OL,7,Ftold ITV News the organisation
OL,8,F"sympathises with the position that
OL,9,Fsome residents are finding themselves"
OL,10,Fas the county continues to face
OL,11,Fextreme housing pressure.
OL,13,FThe spokesperson said it is "committed
OL,14,Fto proving support" however "there is
OL,15,Fa high demand for accommodation,
OL,16,Fincluding our own housing stock,
OL,17,Fproperties that we rent, and other
OL,18,Faccommodation, especially when a
OL,19,Fhousehold requests housing a specific
OL,20,Farea".
