OL,6,FCornwall Council has a duty to provide
OL,7,Ftemporary accommodation to certain
OL,8,Fhouseholds and says it regularly
OL,9,Freviews Personalised Housing Plans and
OL,10,Fhelps residents bid for properties on
OL,11,Fits Homechoice social housing website.
OL,13,FBut says the broader picture of
OL,14,Fhousing availability in Cornwall is
OL,15,Fbleak.
